translation: The incarnation Narsingh was also killed by KAL.

gurmukhi: bfo fMf DwrI ] hixE kwl BwrI ]73]
transliteration: Bado Dound Dhdaroo|| Hanio Kaal Bhdaroo||73||
translation: The incarnation with grinder teeth (i.e. Boar) was killed by mighty KAL.73.
Vaman, the Brahmin incarnation, was killed by KAL.

gurmukhi: mhw m`C muMfM ] PiDE kwl JuMfM ]74]
transliteration: Mahaa Machchh Mounndan|| Phadhio Kaal Jhoundan||74||
translation: The Fish incarnation of spatious mouth, was entrapped by KAL.74.

gurmukhi: ijqy hoie bIqy ] iqqy kwl jIqy ]
transliteration: Jite Hoe Boote|| Tite Kaal Jeete||
translation: All those who had come into being, they were all conquered by KAL.

gurmukhi: ijqy srin jYhYN ] iqiqE rwK lYhYN ]75]
transliteration: Jite Saran(i) Jaihain|| Titio Raakh Laihain||75||
translation: Those who will go under His Refuge, they will all be saved by him.75.

gurmukhi: ibnw srn qw kI n AaurY aupwXM ] khw dyv deIqM khw rMk rwXM ]
transliteration: Binaa Saran Taa K9 Na Aurai Oupaayan|| Kahaa Dev Daootan Kahaa Rank Raayan||
translation: Without coming under His Refuge, there is no other measure for protection, may be a god, demon, pauper or a king.

gurmukhi: khw pwqswhM khw aumrwXM ] ibnw srn qw kI n kotY aupwXM ]76]
transliteration: Kahaa Paasaahan Kahaa Oumraayan|| Binaa Saran Taa Koo Na Kotai Oupaayan||76||
translation: May be the Sovereign and may be the courtiers, without coming under His shelter, millions of measures for protection will be useless. 76.

gurmukhi: ijqy jIv jMqM su dunIAM aupwXM ] sBY AMq kwlM blI kwl GwXM ]
transliteration: Jite Jeev Jantan Su Douneean Oupaayan|| Sabhai Ant Kaalan Balikaal Ghaayan||
translation: All the creatures created by Him in the world will ultimately be killed by the mighty KAL.

gurmukhi: ibnw srn qw kI nhI AOr EtM ] ilKy jMqR kyqy pVHy mMqR kotM ]77]
transliteration: Binaa Saran Taa Koo Nahoo Aur Otan|| Likhe Jantra Kete Padhe Mantra Kotan||77||
translation: There is no other protection without coming under His shelter, even though many Yantras be written and millions of Mantras be recited.77.

gurmukhi: ijqyk rwj rMkXM ] hny su kwl bMkXM ]
transliteration: Jitek Raaj Rankayan|| Hanes U Kaal Bankayan||
translation: All the kings and pupers who have come into being, are sure to be killed by KAL.

gurmukhi: ijqyk lok pwlXM ] indwn kwl dwlXM ]78]
transliteration: Jitek Lok Paalayan|| Nidaan Kaal Daalayan||78||
translation: All the Lokpals, who have come into being, will ultimately be mashed by KAL.78.
